  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RenderDots.LabelScheme  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Render
    Draws a list of Tracer objects in some way using the PGraphics class from Processing.
    RenderClique
    Draws a list of Tracers as a clique (a fully-connected graph), where lines are drawn between each Tracer and every other Tracer
    RenderDots
    Draws a list of Tracers as dots using Processing's point() function.
    RenderDots.Alphabet  
    RenderDots.Enumerate  
    RenderMesh
    Draws a list of Tracer objects as a procedural mesh.
    RenderMetaBalls  
    RenderShape
    Draws a list of Tracer objects as a shape using Processing's beginShape() and endShape() method.
